        <mxCell id="_FUVzvGfVmQXasiZJaL7-19" value="&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;EXPLORATORIES &lt;br&gt;STAKEHOLDER SURVEY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;Should be used with care: Survey asks for prioritization at the final level (sensu cascade mdoel) and for the whole lanndscape, while for soils many services measured are at the regulating/supporting level or at the local and plot scale!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" parent="1" vertex="1">
